data.description:
Unique opportunity to own a single-family home with an auxiliary basement unit. 
• The primary home has three bedrooms, one full bathroom, a kitchen, and laundry. It has new luxury vinyl plank flooring, has been painted throughout, and has a completely renovated bathroom.
• Auxiliary home: 1 bedroom, 1 office, 1 full bathroom, kitchen, and laundry - new luxury vinyl plank flooring, paint throughout, and completely renovated bathroom.
• Newer stainless-steel appliances in both kitchens and laundry in both spaces.
• Tastefully remodeled as a blank slate for your style and furnishings.
• Large backyard oasis with fruit trees and a front/back auto sprinkler system; each unit has a storage shed area 
• 10 minute drive to downtown Denver 
• Close to South Broadway/Santa Fe for numerous restaurants and breweries.  Convenient proximity to Sprouts, Costco, and Target. 
• Easy access to Light Rail. Walking distance to Ruby Hill Park.
